text:
Sense Health (Rotterdam, Netherlands)

Having existed for several years we are changing the mental health care of the Netherlands by providing context aware coaching. We have partnered with the biggest mental health in institute of the Netherlands and are actively looking at new React and React Native developers to join our team!

Skills and expertise - Normalized for keyword search, but this is not the only thing we look for in candidates :)

React / React Native / Typescript / Javascript / CSS

Remote is okay as long as you can overlap a few hours with Dutch time.

https://www.sense-health.com/careers-2/

If you like the mission and are motivated to change the global mental health care, ping me directly.

CTO, Sense Health
